    MECAB_USERDIC=~/.mecab-user.dict

How to rebuild a custom mecab database:

    1. Move the old userdic into a backup

        mv $MECAB_USERDIC $MECAB_USERDIC.bak

    2. Refresh etc/dict.csv

        ./bin/extract-number-words > etc/dict.csv
        mecab-additions >> etc/dict.csv

    3. Generate a new userdic

        `mecab-config --libexecdir`/mecab-dict-index -d`mecab-config --dicdir`/ipadic -u $MECAB_USERDIC -f utf8 -t utf8 etc/dict.csv

    4. Regenerate all morpheme caches (takes a LONG time)

        ./bin/flush-morpheme-caches

